Ollama is a tool that lets you run AI models (like ChatGPT) directly on your own computer.

Easy Example

Normally:

You send request → OpenAI API → get response (internet needed)

With Ollama:

You send request → your local machine → get response

 मतलब AI आपके ही सिस्टम में चलता है

Why Ollama is Useful?
 1. No Internet Needed (after setup)
Once model is downloaded → works offline
 2. Privacy
Your data stays on your system
No data goes to external servers
 3. Free to Use
No API cost
No token billing
 4. Fast for local apps
Especially useful for your projects like:
Chatbot
RAG system
Weather assistant
 How Ollama Works (Simple Flow)
Install Ollama
Download a model (like mistral)
Run model locally
Send prompts → get responses
